metadata.name: RAM Gen 2: RiseAngle Membership NFT
metadata.description:
13 Outstanding NFTs in One Bundle including Metaverse Utility and 3D NFTs!

By owning and holding a RAM Gen 2 NFT, you will gain exclusive access to 12 amazing NFTs from 12 unique NFT collections, over a period of 12 months. RAM also is an NFT itself. RAM Collections will include 3D art, digital comic books, and 2D art, some with utility within the metaverse and some generative.

RAM NFT is the gold standard of future NFT memberships.

Visit https://RiseAngle.com to learn more!
